  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/db60333caecb37d286e9534473ef6dc5.avif?t=1773721524\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras_big/db60333caecb37d286e9534473ef6dc5.avif?t=1773721524 width=800 height=2060 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kingdom's Deck is a game about survival and growing your kingdom. As the ruler of the land, you must navigate the challenges of staying alive, taking care of your people's requirements, building a powerful army, and protecting your fort from approaching threats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/f16a97b0ae6953922a30356fde765c94.webp?t=1773721524\" width=317 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.poster.avif?t=1773721524\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.webm?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.mp4?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of the king, entrusted with the fate of an entire realm. Your journey is guided by your collection of cards, each with a specific purpose. Some cards help you build crucial structures, like food production, resources, and fortifications. Others strengthen your military forces. Your leadership hinges on using these cards wisely, and choosing the right moments and places to play them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/77eb4bd9fd67fbd6d36f0f9a0e46a474.webp?t=1773721524\" width=378 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/b2d90a30c4a4104e1ac5e5a3575eb337.poster.avif?t=1773721524\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/b2d90a30c4a4104e1ac5e5a3575eb337.webm?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/b2d90a30c4a4104e1ac5e5a3575eb337.mp4?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this ever-changing kingdom, peace is a rare luxury, as the relentless darkness continually menaces your realm. Prepare your army for defense and construct impenetrable walls to repel the sieges. Your unwavering determination is what will protect your lands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/f07d91b27405eea5d10fcd4d1f714987.webp?t=1773721524\" width=277 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/644ff8b4ea98fa4bc00fd5e2b76a9378.poster.avif?t=1773721524\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/644ff8b4ea98fa4bc00fd5e2b76a9378.webm?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/644ff8b4ea98fa4bc00fd5e2b76a9378.mp4?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash the elemental forces at your command with powerful spell cards. From fiery infernos to icy blasts, wield magic to turn the tides of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/488b176553582dc263537ef654092729.webp?t=1773721524\" width=449 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/75e1fc1497824b5a28f939120a36bdec.poster.avif?t=1773721524\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/75e1fc1497824b5a28f939120a36bdec.webm?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/75e1fc1497824b5a28f939120a36bdec.mp4?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure the prosperity and growth of your kingdom by managing vital resources effectively. From food to wood, gold, and stone, maintain a careful balance to sustain your people and fuel your ambitions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kingdom's Deck is a game about survival and growing your kingdom. As the ruler of the land, you must navigate the challenges of staying alive, taking care of your people's requirements, building a powerful army, and protecting your fort from approaching threats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/f16a97b0ae6953922a30356fde765c94.webp?t=1773721524\" width=317 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.poster.avif?t=1773721524\" width=640 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.webm?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/6f80ad69ebb1e9d793c086f361fa0596.mp4?t=1773721524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of the king, entrusted with the fate of an entire realm. Your journey is guided by your collection of cards, each with a specific purpose. Some cards help you build crucial structures, like food production, resources, and fortifications. Others strengthen your military forces. Your leadership hinges on using these cards wisely, and choosing the right moments and places to play them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655590/extras/77eb4bd9fd67fbd6d36f0f9a0e46a474.webp?t=1773721524\" width=378 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_im